Preview:
https://soundcloud.com/sound-phenomenon/retro-electro-music-pack-samples

A collection of sixteen exciting retro electronic tracks for use in video games. This music is perfect for high tech settings looking for a synthwave or vaporwave sound. The collection includes a range of moods, from elated and excited, to down and calm, to suspenseful and intense.
